    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The Example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Check a&nbsp;<em>RadioButton </em>to set / change the icon of the <strong>HeaderedPanel </strong>control</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p><strong>HeaderedPanel.Icon</strong> property gets or&nbsp;sets the icon image to display inside the header of <strong>HeaderedPanel </strong>control<br />Property type: Gizmox.WebGUI.Common.Resources.<strong>ResourceHandle</strong></p>]]></Paragraph>
